node.text: Did you purchase from a scam page?✨ On July 21st I showcased one of my newest creations, this beautiful amethyst crystal moon mirror sun catcher. After receiving an amazing response and going viral on both Instagram and TikTok, it caught the attention of online scam shops that this item would be in high demand. In just the month of August, over 122 ads have been published on Facebook, Instagram and TikTok. Receiving thousands of shares, likes and comments. They’re blocking anyone who attempts to tag me and warn potential buyers that it’s a scam. The items on their websites are typically “on sale” for $29.99-$49.99. Their websites usually don’t have contact info, when you click their social media links it leads to nothing. They post fake customer reviews. They never have detailed or multiple photos of the same item they sell.✨So if you purchased this crystal moon sun catcher and it wasn’t from my website sacraluna, then unfortunately it is a scam. There’s been an alarming amount of comments on my page stating my items were never delivered, they’ve arrived broken and it looks nothing like the photo. And all of these purchases were made with scam sites. If this has happened to you, please send me a dm with screenshots so I can locate the specific site , have it removed and assist you in getting a refund. Blessed day everyone!!✨🌞

node.text: Spending the day organizing my studio and shipping out more home decor!!🌸✨I’ve decided it’s time to install cameras in our apartment after multiple items (including orders) have been moved around while I’m out running errands. Boxes that were stacked 3 ft high somehow moving from one room to another. My order list, pens and books. At first I thought someone broke in until I was home alone and started noticing things were still being misplaced as soon as I left the room. And last night I woke up to the strangest noise. I have some old books stored under my bed and I could hear them being knocked over and sliding around on the floor. I thought it was my cats fighting but when I got up I realized they were all sleeping in the kitchen. I’m used to spirits visiting me so it doesn’t make me uncomfortable. But it would be interesting to see it’s activity throughout the day. My cats don’t seem aggravated or alarmed so I’m hoping it a friendly spirit.✨💕

node.text: Good Afternoon!!🌞 Its been such a crazy week here in NYC!! Not only did we get extreme flooding, a random part of my ceiling broke off (thank goodness I wasn’t standing underneath it.) I saved a possum from drowning, a new aura crystal arrived and I’m almost finished packing orders!! Thank you all again for your patience and support!! Tracking numbers are being emailed out daily. If you have any questions about your order feel free to send me a dm for updates. And what do you think about this new aura color??!! It reminds me of a lemon lime!!😍💕

node.text: So in love with this Crystal Moon Sun Catcher Collection!!☀️🔮Featuring my signature amethyst crystal moon mirror and amethyst moon slices!! These beauties sold during my last restock but I cannot wait to make more!!✨It’s been a busy couple weeks wrapping sun catchers and working on pre orders!!! I can’t thank you all enough for your patience and support!! Orders will begin shipping out today, tracking numbers will be sent via email💕 Have a blessed day everyone!!🌿(if you have any questions about your order feel free to send me a dm)

My little helper King!💕 He loves to be in the middle of everything.✨🌸I’ll be spending the day shipping out orders and organizing new stock!! Can’t wait to show everyone the new aura colors I’ve been working on.💕Thank you all again for your love and endless support!!💕PS. I’ve been getting an alarming amount of dm’s and comments stating my items are arriving broken. Only to find out these items were purchased with scam shops using my content, claiming to sell my handmade work. (The only place my items are sold is through my website sacraluna)😵 I will continue to post about this issue since there are new scam sites popping up everyday. A huge thank you to everyone for sending me dms and screenshots to help me get these pages taken down. 💕

node.text:
Good Afternoon!!✨🌞It’s been a busy week wrapping up sun catchers and prepping goodie bags for everyone’s orders!!💕Each order will include one tea light candle, 4 soft touch picture cards, 3 incense cones (if you ordered a cauldron or incense holder) and a bag stuffed with extra crystals! The crystal bags will include a variety of amethyst, rose quartz, grey moonstone, carnelian, peach aventurine, blue tigers eye, garnet, clear quartz and white howlite!✨💕Thank you all so much for your love and support!! 
PS! If you sent an email regarding address updates, shipping or cancelation. Please check your spam folder. I sent out over 40 emails last week and want to make sure they reach everyone!! Have a blessed day!!🌸🌞
